title: Ep 2539 - Sodhis Pacifier
shortDesc: Popatlal wakes up in the middle of the night by a nightmare of the Ghost Bride where she forces him to marry her. Popatlal is forced to tell Chamapklal everything that happened in Mohanlal's apartment.

title: Ep 2540 - The Brave Hearts
shortDesc: Sodhi gets frustrated with Popatlal and Champaklal being petrified by the Ghost Bride that he uses his pacifier which is nothing else but Rum. Sodhi gives a glass of rum to Popatlal but Champaklal grabs the bottles off his hands and drinks it.

title: Ep 2541 - The Meeting
shortDesc: After the drinking fiasco by Popatlal and Champaklal in the society the previous night, Bhide and others decide to have a meeting at Champaklal's house to find a permanent solution to the ghost problem.

title: Ep 2542 - Haunted Flat for Sale
shortDesc: Popatlal narrates his nightmare, in which he married the Ghostly Bride, to the Gokuldham society members.

title: Ep 2543 - The Fear In Gokuldham
shortDesc: Everyone is petrified in the Gokuldham society after Popatlal narrates his dream sequence. The same day a couple who is a potential buyer of Mohanlal's apartment comes to the society to check it out.

title: Ep 2544 - Guru Ghantal
shortDesc: Everyone in Gokuldham society encounters the ghost bride when they accompany the potential buyers of Mohanlal's apartment in the building. Ghost Bride claims that she won't leave the apartment until she finds a suitable guy to get married.

title: Ep 2545 - Beware of Ghost
shortDesc: Amidst the darkness of the night, Jethalal makes an entry into Gokuldham society.  Jethalal is startled by the silence that has gripped the society.  Seeing his house locked, Jethalal calls up Champaklal.

title: Ep 2546 - Jethalals Inspection
shortDesc: Jethalal is finally back in the Gokuldham society and everyone tells him what has been happening in the society in his absence. Jethalal is frightened to the core but acts all tough and decides to check out Mohanlal's apartment

title: Ep 2547 - The Veil Is Raised
shortDesc: Jethalal and the Bride Ghost come face to face with each other after Taarak and Jethalal went to Mohanlal's apartment. Taarak faints after seeing the Ghost but Jethalal is adamant to solve the mystery so he tries to capture the ghost.

title: Ep 2548 - The Truth of the Ghostly Bride
shortDesc: The truth finally comes to light when Vicky and his friends, Pramod and Pakhi, reveal their love story that caused the whole ghostly bride incident.

title: Ep 2549 - Brave Jethalal
shortDesc: Jethalal reveals that he was aware that the ghost was merely a distraction created by Pramod and Pakhi.  But, Iyer isn't convinced and ridicules Jethalal.  Nevertheless, Jethalal's bravery is appreciated by the Gokuldham society members.

title: Ep 2550 - The Ghostly Bride Departs
shortDesc: Pramod and Pakhi are accepted by their family members' thanks to Champaklal's advice to their parents. Later, Bhide sees Sonu chatting with her friends and gets irritated. Madhvi sets things right and asks Bhide to stop controlling their daughter.

title: Ep 2551 - Tapu Sena Upto Something
shortDesc: Jethalal calls up Daya and tells her how much everyone is missing her and asks her to come back soon. Madhvi Ji prepares breakfast for Tapu Sena as they inform Bhide about the meeting for the upcoming festival.

title: Ep 2552 - The Important Meeting
shortDesc: Tapu Sena arrives in the society's main hall and prepares for the meeting. Jethalal is late for the meeting yet again and Bhide is furious so he decides to teach Jethalal a lesson.

title: Ep 2553 - Bhides Dream
shortDesc: The preparations for the Ganesh Chaturthi festival are going on in the Gokuldham Society and Tapu Sena is handling everything perfectly. Champaklal decides that Dr. Hathi and his wife will be the first ones to perform the pooja.
